      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered icon, maintained to a fastidious standard. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six delivers linear power through its six individual throttle bodies, with the Double VANOS system functioning perfectly across the entire rev range. The chassis has been professionally reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a fresh clutch and a factory limited-slip differential. This vehicle exhibits zero oil consumption and has had the critical rod bearing service performed preventatively. Finished in concours-quality paint with a flawless interior, this is a turn-key collector-grade machine optimized for the purist driver.",
